edu.cmu.sphinx.frontend

Interface Data

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Scoreable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataEndSignal, DataStartSignal, DoubleData, FloatData, Signal, SpeechClassifiedData, SpeechEndSignal, SpeechStartSignal, Token

    public interface Data
extends java.io.Serializable
    Implements the interface for all Data objects that passes between DataProcessors. Subclass of Data can contain the actual data, or be a signal (e.g., data start, data end, speech start, speech end).
    See Also:
    Data, FrontEnd
